          "text": "Artificial intelligence has revolutionized many industries. Healthcare professionals use AI to diagnose diseases more accurately. _____ AI helps financial institutions detect fraud and manage risk. _____ concerns about job displacement and privacy have emerged. _____ these challenges, many experts believe the benefits of AI outweigh the potential drawbacks.",
          "word_count": 45
